    <div class="story__element__text">
        <p>
          <b>Redressal Mechanism:</b> Any complaints. or concerns with regards to the processing of information provided by you or breach of these terms shall be immediately informed to the designated Grievance Officer as mentioned below via in writing by email / post / courier to grievance@bloombergquint.com or
